<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{you get a call from rose?}
<C>__{lazarus}
<D>__{this ain't got nothin' to do with that woman. just don't want nobody around me now.}
<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{somethin' wrong with ya phone? been callin' the last few days.}
<A>__{r.l. stops in his tracks as lazarus pulls out his hunting rifle from the rack behind his seat in his truck.}
<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{goin' dove huntin'?}
