<D>__{you gotta go, r.l.. i ain't foolin' this time.}
<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{you sayin' that gun's for me if i don't?}
<P>__{(laz can't answer)}
<D>__{spell it out, laz. man big enough to pull a gun best have a tongue in his mouth if he ain't got a brain in his head.}
<A>__{laz is struggling. the rifle feels suddenly strange to him.}
<C>__{lazarus}
<D>__{you ain't gonna talk me outta shit no more. i got my mind made up and i ain't gonna be moved on this.}
