<P>__{(still stepping closer)}
<D>__{or what?}
<C>__{lazarus}
<D>__{i told you to turn back!}
<A>__{r.l. pushes his chest up against the rifle and shouts back.}
<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{you go'on and shoot me, killa!}
<A>__{laz's heart is breaking. he is pointing a gun at his only friend. r.l. snatches the rifle out of laz's hands.}
<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{ought'a stomp yo ass pointing this at me.}
