<D>__{dammit, laz... we may not be blood. but we sucked off the same old nurse since the day we was slapped on the ass. and you gonna point a gun at me?}
<A>__{a tear rolls down laz's cheek. the shame is unbearable.}
<C>__{r.l.}
<D>__{if you in some trouble, than we gonna figure somethin' out. you and me.}
